### Files Modified

1. **`libs/custom-ner-loader.js`**
   - Refactored `predict()` to detect long documents
   - Added `predictSingleChunk()` for documents ≤512 tokens
   - Added `predictWithSlidingWindow()` for long documents
   - Added `createChunks()` for chunk creation
   - Added `processChunk()` for individual chunk inference
   - Added `mergeEntities()` for deduplication
   - Added `entitiesOverlap()` for overlap detection

